A 787 FINAL ASSEMBLY PLANT IN NORTH CHARLESTON, SOUTH CAROLINA. ON DECEMBER 8, 2011 THE IAM REQUESTED THAT ITS CHARGE BE WITHDRAWN, AND ON DECEMBER 9, 2011 THE NLRB WITHDREW THE CHARGE AND DISMISSED THE COMPLAINT.

