N&SS REVENUES

DECREASED 8% IN 2011 AND 13% IN 2010. THE DECREASE OF $782 MILLION IN 2011 IS PRIMARILY DUE TO $577 MILLION OF LOWER REVENUES ON THE BCTM PROGRAM WHICH WAS TERMINATED FOR CONVENIENCE DURING 2011. LOWER REVENUES ON THE GROUND-BASED MIDCOURSE DEFENSE

