WOULD EXTEND THE CREDIT. IF THE RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT CREDIT IS NOT EXTENDED THERE WOULD BE AN UNFAVORABLE IMPACT TO OUR 2012 EFFECTIVE INCOME TAX RATE. FOR THE YEARS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2011, 2010 AND 2009, THE RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT

