THE FOLLOWING ASSUMPTIONS, WHICH ARE THE WEIGHTED AVERAGE FOR ALL PLANS, ARE USED TO CALCULATE THE BENEFIT OBLIGATION AT DECEMBER 31 OF EACH YEAR AND THE NET

PERIODIC BENEFIT COST FOR THE SUBSEQUENT YEAR.

